🗝️ 📚
🧩 special_factorial(n) 👉
   fact_i ⬅️ 1
   special_fact ⬅️ 1
   i ⬅️ 1
   🌀 n 👉
      fact_i ⬅️ 積(fact_i, i)
      special_fact ⬅️ 積(special_fact, fact_i)
      i ⬆️
   🔚
   ✅ special_fact
🔚
>>> special_factorial(4) 
288
>>> special_factorial(4) 
288
>>> special_factorial(5) 
34560
>>> special_factorial(7) 
125411328000
>>> special_factorial(1) 
1